        <abstract>
            <p>Glad to have JJW’s opinion on nest-building. Wallace’s view [that skill is learned] is opposed to many facts.</p>
            <p>Asks JJW about birds and their behaviour.</p>
            <p>Wants information on the first plumage of different breeds of canaries.</p>
        </abstract>
